\q2 вүҲandВҰ142142 Sha'ul's swordВҰ142142 didn't \add вүҲfail on its strikes\add*.
\b
\q1
\v 23 Sha'ulВҰ142148 and Yonatan were lovedвҖ”
\q2 вүҲthey pleasedВҰ142151 the people.
\q2 and even atВҰ142152 their deathВҰ142153 they weren't separatedВҰ142155.
