\s4 Full kingdom
\r (1 Chr. 17:16-27)
\p
\v 17 \add вүҲSo\add* NatanВҰ145176 \add вүҲpassed all of that onto\add* DavidВҰ145179,
\v 18 and KingВҰ145183 DavidВҰ145184 wentВҰ145182 and satВҰ145185 \add вүҲin frontВҰ145186\add* of Yahweh and saidВҰ145188, вҖңWho am I, my masterВҰ145191 Yahweh, and \add вүҲhow important is my family\add* that youВҰ145196 have broughtВҰ145196 me to \add вүҲthis point\add*?
\v 19 \add вүҲButВҰ145201 that was just minor to you,\add* my master YahwehВҰ145205. You also spokeВҰ145207 aboutВҰ145214 \add вүҲthe distantВҰ145214 future for my descendants\add*.
\v 20 What more can \add I,\add* DavidВҰ145224 sayВҰ145226 to you? \add вүҲButВҰ145221\add* my masterВҰ145233 YahwehВҰ145233, you yourself knowВҰ145229 your servantВҰ145232.
\v 21 You've done all these incredible things \add вүҲin order to fulfil what youВҰ145239 said and to fulfil your own desires\add*, and then \add вүҲrevealed them to\add* your servantВҰ145248.
\v 22 That'sВҰ145255 why you'reВҰ145253 incredible, YahwehВҰ145254 my godВҰ145261, \add вүҲand so\add* there's no one like you. There'sВҰ145250 no godВҰ145261 exceptВҰ145262 youвҖ”\add вүҲthat's what we keep hearing about\add*.
\v 23 \add вүҲWhat other nation\add* is like your people, YisraelВҰ145271вҖ”one nation on the earthВҰ145274 thatВҰ145275 \add *you\add* went to redeemВҰ145279 for \add вүҲyourself\add* as a peopleвҖ”\add вүҲrescuing\add* you from EgyptВҰ145296 and its godsВҰ145298? \add You\add* \add вүҲmade a reputationВҰ145285 for yourself\add* and \add вүҲdid amazing and scary things for your nation in frontВҰ145291\add* of your people\x + \xo 7:23: \xt Deu 4:34.\x*
\v 24 You establishedВҰ145300 \add us\add* Israelis as your \add own\add* people forever, andВҰ145300 you yourself YahwehВҰ145314 became \add вүҲour\add* GodВҰ145317.
\p
\v 25 вҖңAnd now, YahwehВҰ145321 GodВҰ145322, the \add вүҲpromise you made\add* concerningВҰ145329 your servantВҰ145328 and his \add вүҲdescendants\add*, and do just as you have spoken and \add вүҲmake it come true into the future\add*.
\v 26 May your \add вүҲreputationВҰ145341 be good\add* forever, \add with people\add* saying, вҖҳCommander YahwehВҰ145346 is GodВҰ145348 over YisraelВҰ145351,вҖҷ andВҰ145340 the \add вүҲdynasty\add* of your servantВҰ145353 DavidВҰ145354 will be establishedВҰ145356 \add вүҲunder youВҰ145357\add*,
\v 27 because you, commanderВҰ145363 YahwehВҰ145362 are Yisrael'sВҰ145365 godВҰ145364. You have \add вүҲtold\add* your servant, вҖҳI will buildВҰ145373 a \add вүҲdynasty\add* for you.вҖҷ \add вүҲThat's why\add* your servant has foundВҰ145379 \add вүҲthe courage\add* to pray this prayerВҰ145388.
\p
\v 28 вҖң\add вүҲSoВҰ145391\add* now, my masterВҰ145393 YahwehВҰ145393, you are GodВҰ145398, and \add вүҲyou do what you say\add*, and you have said these goodВҰ145408 thingsВҰ145408 concerning your servantВҰ145405.
\v 29 NowВҰ145425, \add вүҲif itВҰ145428 pleases you,\add* bless your servant's \add вүҲextended family\add* forever, because you yourself, my masterВҰ145424 YahwehВҰ145424, have spokenВҰ145426, andВҰ145411 from your blessing, your servant's \add вүҲfamily\add* will be blessed forever.вҖқ
\c 8
\s1 David's victories
