\v 25 \add вүҲNow\add* AbshalomВҰ148940 \add вүҲwas admired as the most handsomeВҰ148946 manВҰ148944\add* in all YisraelВҰ148949вҖ”from the \add вүҲtop\add* of his headВҰ148955 to the \add вүҲbottom\add* of his feet, \add вүҲyou wouldn't be able to find a blemishВҰ148960 on his skin\add*.
\v 26 He \add вүҲhad his hair cut once a year when it got too heavyВҰ148976 onВҰ148962 him, andВҰ148962 when the hair was weighed using standard weights, it would be over twoВҰ148984 kilograms\add*.
\v 27 AbshalomВҰ148990 had threeВҰ148991 sonsВҰ148992 andВҰ148989 a daughterВҰ148993 named TamarВҰ148996вҖ”a very attractive womanВҰ148999.
