\v 32 вҖңListen, I \add вүҲtried to contact\add* you,вҖқ AbshalomВҰ149083 \add вүҲreplied\add*. вҖңI asked you to come here so that I could send you to the king \add вүҲto ask what the point was of bringing me here from GeshurВҰ149103\add* \add if I can't see him\add*вҖ”\add вүҲI might as well have stayed back\add* there. \add вүҲSoВҰ149082\add* now, \add вүҲhelp me to get invited to see\add* the king, andВҰ149082 then if \add вүҲI'm considered guilty of a crime\add*, then let him kill me.вҖқ
