\v 33 \add вүҲSoВҰ149122\add* YoavВҰ149123 wentВҰ149134 and informed the king, and he calledВҰ149130 for AbshalomВҰ149133. \add вүҲWhenВҰ149148 he entered\add*, he \add вүҲknelt and bowedВҰ149138 his face\add* to the ground \add вүҲin frontВҰ149144 of\add* the king, and thenВҰ149122 the king kissedВҰ149146 \add *him\add*.
