\v 13 \add Eventually,\add* \add вүҲsomeone wentВҰ149389\add* andВҰ149389 told DavidВҰ149393, вҖңThe \add вүҲloyalty of the IsraeliВҰ149399 people is turning towards\add* AbshalomВҰ149401.вҖқ
