\v 14 \add вүҲSoВҰ149403\add* DavidВҰ149404 told his servantsВҰ149407, вҖң\add вүҲPack up quickly and let's get out of here, or else we won'tВҰ149415 be able\add* to escapeВҰ149420 from AbshalomВҰ149422. \add вүҲBe fast inВҰ149411 case he's heading here soon\add* and overtakesВҰ149428 us. \add вүҲThat would be a massacre and the whole cityВҰ149435 would die from their swordsВҰ149438\add*.вҖқ
