\p
\v 30 \add вүҲAs\add* DavidВҰ149758 was going up the MtВҰ149760. of Olives, he was walkingВҰ149769 barefootВҰ149770 with his head covered. He was weeping as were the peopleВҰ149773 with himвҖ”they \add too\add* had their heads covered andВҰ149758 were weeping.
