\v 1 DavidВҰ149906 \add вүҲhadn't gone far past the summitВҰ149909 when\add*, wow, he was meet by Mefiboshet's servantВҰ149912 Tsiva with a pair of saddledВҰ149919 donkeysВҰ149918 \add вүҲloaded with\add* twoВҰ149921 hundred breadВҰ149922 rolls, one hundred \add вүҲcakes\add* of raisinsВҰ149924, one hundred \add pieces\add* of fresh fruitВҰ149926, andВҰ149906 a \add вүҲleather container\add* of wine.\x + \xo 16:1: \xt 2Sam 9:9-10.\x*
