\v 22 \add вүҲSoВҰ150350\add* they \add вүҲset up\add* a tentВҰ150352 for AbshalomВҰ150351 on the \add palace\add* roofВҰ150355 andВҰ150356 \add *he\add* \add вүҲhad sex\add* with his father'sВҰ150361 slave-wives \add вүҲwhere everyoneВҰ150350 would know what was going on\add*.\x + \xo 16:22: \xt 2Sam 12:11-12.\x*
