\p
\v 1 Then Ahitofel \add вүҲasked\add* AbshalomВҰ150395, вҖңPlease, let me chooseВҰ150396 twelve thousandВҰ150401 men, then let me \add вүҲgo\add* and pursueВҰ150404 afterВҰ150405 DavidВҰ150407 tonight.
