\p
\v 7 вҖңThis timeВҰ150511, Ahitofel's suggestion isn'tВҰ150503 \add such\add* goodВҰ150505 adviceВҰ150506,вҖқ Hushay \add вүҲreplied\add*.
\v 8 You yourself know your father and his menвҖ”\add and do remember\add* that they're \add вүҲpowerful warriorsВҰ150525\add*вҖ”they're \add вүҲstill furious\add* like a bear in the countrysideВҰ150532 \add вүҲthat's been robbedВҰ150531 of its cubs\add*. And your father is an \add experienced\add* man of war, and he won'tВҰ150536 spend the nightВҰ150537 \add there\add* with the peopleВҰ150540.
