\p
\v 15 Then Hushay told the \add two\add* priestsВҰ150719 TsadokВҰ150715 and Evyatar what Ahitofel had suggested to AbshalomВҰ150726 and the IsraeliВҰ150728 eldersВҰ150728 and \add вүҲwhat he'd countered it with\add*.
