\p
\v 17 \add Their sons\add* Yonatan and Ahimaats were waiting atВҰ150762 Eyn-Rogel \add вүҲwhere\add* a female servantВҰ150766 would come and \add вүҲpass the message onto\add* them, because it \add вүҲwouldn't be safe for them\add* to be seenВҰ150777 enteringВҰ150778 the cityВҰ150779. ThenВҰ150759 they themselves would goВҰ150765 and inform KingВҰ150772 DavidВҰ150773.
