\p
\v 1 DavidВҰ151036 \add вүҲdivided his warriorsВҰ151039 into units\add* and appointed commanders of hundredsВҰ151047 and of thousandsВҰ151045.
\v 2 \add *He\add* \add вүҲsentВҰ151049 them out in three groups under\add* Yoav, AbishaiВҰ151060 (son of Yoav's brotherВҰ151064 Tseruyah) andВҰ151049 IttaiВҰ151068 (the GittiteВҰ151069), thenВҰ151049 \add вүҲpromised that he'd also join them in battle\add*.
