\v 3 \add вүҲButВҰ151083\add* the peopleВҰ151084 \add вүҲcomplained\add*, вҖң\add No,\add* don'tВҰ151085 goВҰ151086 out, because if we \add вүҲhave to\add* flee, they won't \add вүҲbe worried about\add* us. \add вүҲEven\add* if half of us dieВҰ151099, they won't \add вүҲbe worried about\add* us, because you \add вүҲcount more to them than tenВҰ151110 thousandВҰ151111 of us\add*. \add вүҲSoВҰ151083\add* it's better that you \add вүҲstay to\add* helpВҰ151120 us from the cityВҰ151119.вҖқ
