\v 6 SoВҰ151178 \add David's\add* peopleВҰ151179 wentВҰ151178 out to the countrysideВҰ151180 to meet \add the rest of\add* YisraelВҰ151182. The battleВҰ151184 was inВҰ151185 the EfrayimВҰ151186 forestВҰ151185
