\p
\v 18 \add вүҲDuring his lifetimeВҰ151433,\add* Abshalom had setup a pillar inВҰ151433 the King's Valley because \add вүҲhe had no sons to preserve his name\add*. He \add вүҲput his name onВҰ151433\add* the pillar and it's known as вҖҳAbshalom'sВҰ151428 handвҖҷ to this dayВҰ151461.
