\v 19 Then Tsadok'sВҰ151468 son Ahimaats \add вүҲrequested\add*, вҖңPlease, let me runВҰ151470 and let me take the newsВҰ151472 to the kingВҰ151475, because YahwehВҰ151479 has \add вүҲrescued\add* himВҰ151478 from his enemiesВҰ151481.вҖқ
