\v 20 вҖңFar be it, far be it for me that I would \add вүҲdestroyВҰ153284 or wipe it out\add*,вҖқ YoavВҰ153274 replied.
\v 21 \add вүҲThat's not what we're here for\add*. \add We're here\add* for a man from the EfrayimВҰ153293 hills named Sheva, the son of Bikri. He \add вүҲtook a stand\add* against the kingВҰ153301вҖ”against DavidВҰ153302. \add Just\add* \add вүҲhandВҰ153300 him over to us, and then we'll leave your\add* cityВҰ153309.вҖқ
