\v 20 InВҰ153910 a \add вүҲdifferent\add* battleВҰ153890 inВҰ153891 GatВҰ153891, there was a \add вүҲfierce manВҰ153894\add* there withВҰ153891 \add вүҲsix fingersВҰ153897 on each handВҰ153898 and six toesВҰ153899 on each footВҰ153900\add* who was also a descendant of the giantsВҰ153910,
