\v 22 ThoseВҰ153930 fourВҰ153927 \add >men\add* were descendants of the giantsВҰ153930 inВҰ153931 GatВҰ153931, \add вүҲbutВҰ153932\add* theyВҰ153929 were \add вүҲkilled\add* by DavidВҰ153935 and his \add вүҲmen\add*.
